# Luxury Salon Website - Walkthrough

I have completed the top page for the luxury salon "LUMIÈRE".

## Features
- **Minimalist Design**: Used generous whitespace and elegant serif fonts (Mincho/Garamond).
- **Responsive**: Adjusted layout for mobile devices (horizontal text fallback).
- **Smooth Animations**: Added fade-in effects for text and buttons.
- **Fallback Hero**: Due to quota limits, I created a custom SVG placeholder that mimics a soft, elegant background.

## Key Files
- [index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury-salon-website/index.html): Main structure.
- [style.css](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury-salon-website/style.css): All styles and animations.
- [assets/hero_bg.svg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury-salon-website/assets/hero_bg.svg): The abstract background asset.

## How to View
Open [luxury-salon-website/index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury-salon-website/index.html) in your browser.

